Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: logz
Version: 0.12
Summary: easy log use for extra infos
Home-page: https://github.com/hanzhichao/logz
Author: Han Zhichao
Author-email: superhin@126.com
License: MIT license
Description: # log
        
        > pip install logz
        
        
        ```python
        from logz import log
        
        log.file = 'logs/%Y-%m-%d.log'
        log.level = 'info'
        log.format = '%(levelname)s %(name)s %(user)s %(message)s'
        log.file = '%Y-%m-%d.html'
        log.debug({'foo': 'bar'}, indent=2)
        log.info("hello", extra={'user': 'hanzhichao'})
        
        ```
        
        output:
        ```
        2019-12-09 19:30:16,419 DEBUG log None ->
        {
          "foo": "bar"
        }
        2019-12-09 19:30:16,419 INFO log hanzhichao hello
        ```
        
